languages.text: Пустотный корабль подобен целому городу: его населяют тысячи человек, большинство из которых — бесправная чернь, легко заменимый рабочий ресурс. Единственное предназначение простолюдинов — это тяжелый труд во имя ненасытных аппетитов флагмана.

languages.text: A voidship is like a city unto itself, inhabited by thousands of people, most of whom are disenfranchised rabble providing an easily replaceable workforce. The common folk's only mission in life is to toil away in the name of the flagship's insatiable demands.

languages.text: Una nave del vacío es como una ciudad con miles de habitantes, la mayoría plebe descastada que proporciona una mano de obra fácilmente reemplazable. La única misión en la vida del populacho es dejarse la piel para satisfacer las demandas insaciables de la nave insignia.
languages.original_text: A voidship is like a city unto itself, inhabited by thousands of people, most of whom are disenfranchised rabble providing an easily replaceable workforce. The common folk's only mission in life is to toil away in the name of the flagship's insatiable demands.

languages.text: ヴォイドシップはそれ自体が一つの都市のようなものであり、何千人もの人々が住んでいるが、その大半は権利を剥奪された大衆であり、簡単に取り換え可能な労働力となっている。一般の人々の人生の唯一の使命は、船の無尽蔵な要求に応じて働き続けることである。
languages.original_text: A voidship is like a city unto itself, inhabited by thousands of people, most of whom are disenfranchised rabble providing an easily replaceable workforce. The common folk's only mission in life is to toil away in the name of the flagship's insatiable demands.

languages.text: 虚空舰本身就像一座悬浮在宇宙中的城市，居住着成千上万的船员。其中绝大部分船员都是没有任何权利可言的底层人民，这些人是最基本的劳动力，很容易被其他人取代。对这些人而言，他们人生唯一的使命就是不辞辛苦地劳作，满足这艘旗舰贪得无厌的需求。
languages.original_text: A voidship is like a city unto itself, inhabited by thousands of people, most of whom are disenfranchised rabble providing an easily replaceable workforce. The common folk's only mission in life is to toil away in the name of the flagship's insatiable demands.

languages.text: Ein Raumschiff gleicht einer Stadt mit Tausenden von weitgehend rechtlosen Bewohnern, die als leicht ersetzbare Arbeitskräfte dienen. Die einzige Aufgabe des gemeinen Volkes ist die Befriedigung der unstillbaren Begierden des Flaggschiffs.
languages.original_text: A voidship is like a city unto itself, inhabited by thousands of people, most of whom are disenfranchised rabble providing an easily replaceable workforce. The common folk's only mission in life is to toil away in the name of the flagship's insatiable demands.

languages.text: Les vaisseaux spatiaux sont de véritables villes peuplées de milliers d'habitants, pour la plupart des prolétaires privés de droits qui fournissent une main-d'œuvre facilement remplaçable. Ces gens du commun n'ont qu'une seule et unique raison d'être : subvenir aux besoins insatiables du vaisseau.

Uçsuz gemisi, kendi içinde bir şehir gibidir. İçerisinde binlerce insanı barındırır ve bunların çoğu da yerlerine kolayca yenileri konulabilen iş gücünü oluşturan, haklarından mahrum edilmiş ayaktakımıdır. Sıradan halkın hayattaki tek misyonu, sancak gemisinin bitmek bilmez taleplerini karşılayabilme uğruna çalışıp didinmektir.
